author: hiranya
msg: Using the Commons-IO API to carry out file operations in the Multi xml config serializer. The Commons-IO API providers better and consistent file system operations both on Unix and Windows.

author: stsp
msg: (make_tunnel): Tell users how to get informative error messages
from SSH to help debug connection problems. For instance, SSH
can fail to connect because a key file has insecure permissions,
but the corresponding error message is not printed by SSH because
Subversion passes the -q flag to SSH by default.
